{"tid":2139470,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"而家睇翻蘋果廣告製作公司嘅廣告真心覺得有啲邪","createTime":"2020-08-04T09:51:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-16T09:05:18.000Z","uid":364629,"like":7,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3b8555ec5b2a561ce4d3b973a35a307b83ba68ca","tid":2139470,"uid":364629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T09:51:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wJRGXXM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwJRGXXM.gif&h=cafee189&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n02年尾至03年過年前期間播出類似<br />\n蘋果廣告製作公司風格嘅廣告<br />\n之後冇幾耐香港爆發SARS 反23條 <br />\n<br />\n18年聖誕節期間播出呢個廣告之後<br />\n19年6月就直接爆發反送中運動<br />\n20年後直頭爆發埋沙士升級版<br />\n武漢肺炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係有啲邪 唔係講笑<br />\n廣告播完之後冇耐<br />\n就硬係有啲不幸大事發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望以後呢啲咁嘅廣告唔好再出現啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70501e3d2a7f8ed58942f278d1209765c211fbf2","tid":2139470,"uid":364629,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T09:52:49.000Z","msg":"有冇人都係咁認為 真係好撚恐怖<br />\n有啲嘢真係唔到你唔信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea18a08c28dd2afdeda2c279fd0624bb905dee52","tid":2139470,"uid":364629,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T09:56:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fb7c79d73fb95d6815e1b4977b50d56b1d3c3c1","tid":2139470,"uid":183576,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T09:58:17.000Z","msg":"想同高手紹做愛"},{"pid":"67b4ddf45751ba12fb7bc85d18dd5ce5c4b2d4d0"